weka.classifiers.functions.gmlvq.core.cost

Class ConfusionMatrix

  • java.lang.Object
    • weka.classifiers.functions.gmlvq.core.cost.ConfusionMatrix
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class ConfusionMatrix
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Provides the implementation of any confusion matrix based cost function. These costs can only be computed for cases where 2 classes are present. Each cost function is interlinked to an update rule. TODO: implement safety net for non-2-class-problems (safety = mucho exceptiano)
    Author:
    S
